  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p class=\"description\"><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl139_LabelType\">Even though you are a trained combatant, proficient with any number of weapons, you don&rsquo;t relish killing your enemies. It&rsquo;s not that you&rsquo;re afraid of seeing blood, but rather that disabling a foe is superior to killing someone capable of admitting defeat.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl139_LabelType\">When using a melee weapon that deals lethal damage to instead deal nonlethal damage, you take only a &ndash;2 penalty instead of &ndash;4.</span></p>",
